{"tid":1434465,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得係時候要發動網絡聖戰","createTime":"2019-08-08T19:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:39.000Z","uid":163171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"555f0ea3a4f275807bcb514c0429398ebb3c2a02","tid":1434465,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:22:01.000Z","msg":"喺呢個時候仲撐警、撐政府、撐共嘅人大多數都係廢老、廢中或者係蝗蟲。佢哋喺數年間開始步入網絡世界，無論係facebook、whatsapp、各大討論區，都充斥住各種紅媒。<br />\n<br />\n老實說，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">網絡</span></span>係造就住我哋無大台嘅優良局面，係我地最大嘅武器同時，亦都係最利害嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙面刃</span></span>；假如左派勢力都享用到呢把利刃繼而形成一種龐大團體，對我地非常不利，630、810嘅撐警活動就係好例子。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然依家出現好多假膠group企圖混淆班老嘢視聽，但其實最後都係同普通group一樣自己人圍爐取暖；好開心見到各位文宣巴打出到咁多精美蓮花圖，子彈我地已經有，係時候要發動攻勢，攻陷各個紅媒，令佢地嘅page再無討論價值同空間；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">基本戰略：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n喺紅媒出現嘅大多數都係無乜文化嘅蝗蟲，大家可以用文化攻擊；例如連繁體字、粵語都未學得好，字又打錯嘅蝗蟲，出黎獻醜？<br />\n<br />\n對住班奶共知識分子，可以用數據、新聞證據同龐大文字嚟攻陷佢地，香港發展到呢一步，無論民生、社會、政治、經濟、體制，都充斥住各種荒謬，基本上企喺香港人角度，無可能講唔贏呢班冚家剷。<br />\n<br />\n對住紅底親人，請善用各種蓮花圖，用愛去感化佢地，一家人千萬唔好傷和氣。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位冷氣軍士、建盤戰士，係時候出動！<br />\nWE CONNECT!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cfbbc651e487af94f87ee65ca6303cc309cf7e","tid":1434465,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:22:49.000Z","msg":"自推100萬次"},{"pid":"131585439aef44c69d767e4282113b3a56cc859e","tid":1434465,"uid":274792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UWNBohJmKYs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUWNBohJmKYs&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCKZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=9f6a8876\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UWNBohJmKYs</a><br />\n借位俾大家睇下"},{"pid":"b1839288f56bcaebc1541749bc5c0a425331ef23","tid":1434465,"uid":277560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:28:47.000Z","msg":"話聲俾大家知<br />\n銀髮族星期六會去遞信請願呀<br />\nWe connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3T8NPEd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3T8NPEd.jpg&h=a4919402&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8cb7bbc9081283f99c327406c6b3383f9d93bc0","tid":1434465,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:52:25.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"a77108d4cf8c219b12f551a91edf4a9650de6d0b","tid":1434465,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀"},{"pid":"b6eaaca1c3b805c142328142d88496f5d1276ace","tid":1434465,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:19:34.000Z","msg":"無人覺得有需要？"},{"pid":"25993d5d0810d2ee749d6284d98414e6293b6f39","tid":1434465,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8106985894453dbdf9337cce141c05f6e9584e6c","tid":1434465,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:33:28.000Z","msg":"睇見紅媒d page就嬲，但一條友去只會被圍，有一合擊？"},{"pid":"b22afce933c39d10641cbe663f055f499ef63117","tid":1434465,"uid":1631